#
# ROOM LAYOUT
#   meridian_claims_suite (start) → north → meridian_evidence_archive (PIN locked)
#
# DEPLOYMENT
#   Copy to: BreakEscape/scenarios/sis03_cyber_insurance/scenario.json.erb
